                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The vinlach's warbling voices are a mockery of the rhythmic sound of a flight of whippoorwills whistling away, sending chills into the hearts of those who hear them. A living creature that begins its turn within 30 feet of a vinlach must succeed at a @Check[will|dc:23] save or gain weakness 5 to spirit damage until the start of its next turn, as its soul aches to flee its body and retreat along the River of Souls to find peace from the unnerving cacophony.</p>"
